description:
This is a 24 minute workout called '*NEW* Insane 20 Minute Elliptical Workout - HIIT Workout' from the channel AbundantYou with Dr Kevin.
The workout falls under Cardio/Elliptical and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Firestarter vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Dr. Kevin from abundantyou.com gives you another follow-along NEW insane 20 minute HIIT workout using an elliptical. This elliptical workout will push your to your MAXIMUM.  #EllipticalWorkout #HIITWorkout #Elliptical

An elliptical workout machine with handles is one of the few cardio machines that can provide you with both an upper- and lower-body workout. This means its the perfect choice to continue training your body without the wear and tear that comes with high-impact exercises. I love working out on an elliptical machine!
